    <item>
      <title>Quikrete 获得 92 亿美元融资，超级债务交易再度兴起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/mega-debt-deals-return-with-quikrete-s-9-2-billion-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[92 亿美元的债务方案将为 Quikrete Holdings Inc. 收购 Summit Materials Inc. 提供融资，这表明华尔街期待已久的一个愿望即将实现：大规模收购的回归。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/mega-debt-deals-return-with-quikrete-s-9-2-billion-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 15:13:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗利用特别奖金留住财富银行家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-25/citi-s-new-strategy-for-retailing-wealth-bankers-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团在重组其财富管理业务的同时，还推出了一项新策略来留住高级银行家——为数十名员工提供特别留任奖金。彭博社的 Todd Gillespie 在“彭博未平仓合约”中详细报道了此事。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-25/citi-s-new-strategy-for-retailing-wealth-bankers-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 15:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅西百货因数百万美元隐性费用推迟盈利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-25/macy-s-delays-earnings-after-millions-of-hidden-expenses-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梅西百货公司表示，该公司将推迟发布第三季度财报，此前一项调查发现，一名员工“故意”编造错误的会计应计分录，以掩盖多年来累计约 1.32 亿至 1.54 亿美元的配送费用。彭博电视台的 Emily Cohn 对此进行了报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-25/macy-s-delays-earnings-after-millions-of-hidden-expenses-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 15:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>咖啡价格因供应担忧飙升至 1997 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/consumers-face-pricier-coffee-as-arabica-hits-highest-since-1997</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对主要种植户作物产量的担忧，纽约咖啡期货价格攀升至 1997 年以来的最高水平，有可能进一步提高烘焙商和消费者的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/consumers-face-pricier-coffee-as-arabica-hits-highest-since-1997</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 14:30:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
